//	* Rate limiting and CORS
//	* CADF-compatible audit trail
//	* Sentry error reporting
//	* OpenStack-style CLI client (`archerctl`)
//
//	### Supported Backends
//	* **F5 BigIP** — provisioned via the `archer-f5-agent`
